]]'' ||Lucy Barrows ||\n|-\n| ''[[True Heart Susie]]'' || True Heart Susie||\n|-\n| ''[[The Greatest Question]]'' ||Nellie Jarvis ||\n|}\n\n===1920s===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Year\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Title\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Role\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Note\n|-\n|rowspan=2|1920 || ''[[Remodeling Her Husband]]''||{{n/a}} ||Director only/'''Lost film''' \n|-\n| ''[[Way Down East]]'' ||Anna Moore ||\n|-\n| 1921 ||''[[Orphans of the Storm]]'' || Henriette Girard||\n|-\n|1923 || ''[[The White Sister (1923 film)|The White Sister]]'' ||Angela Chiaromonte ||\n|-\n|1924 || ''[[Romola (film)|Romola]]'' ||Romola ||\n|-\n|1925 || ''[[Ben-Hur: A Tale of the Christ (1925 film)|Ben-Hur: A Tale of the Christ]]'' || Chariot Race Spectator|| Cameo (Uncredited)\n|-\n|rowspan=2|1926 || ''[[La Boh\u00e8me (1926 film)|La Boh\u00e8me]]'' ||Mimi ||\n|-\n| ''[[The Scarlet Letter (1926 film)|The Scarlet Letter]]''|| Hester Prynne||\n|-\n|rowspan=2|1927 || ''[[Annie Laurie (1927 film)|Annie Laurie]]''||Annie Laurie ||\n|-\n| ''[[The Enemy (1927 film)|The Enemy]]'' ||Pauli Arndt ||'''Partially extant'''\n|-\n|1928 || ''[[The Wind (1928 film)|The Wind]]'' ||Letty ||Her final silent film role\n|}\n\n==Post Silent==\n\n===1930s===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Year\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Title\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Role\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Note\n|-\n|1930 || ''[[One Romantic Night]]'' ||Princess Alexandra || Her first talkie film role\n|-\n|1933 || ''[[His Double Life]]'' ||Alice Chalice ||\n|}\n\n===1940s===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Year\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Title\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Role\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Note\n|-\n|1942|| ''[[Commandos Strike at Dawn]]'' ||Mrs. Bergesen ||\n|-\n|1943 || ''[[Top Man (film)|Top Man]]'' ||Beth Warren || Alternate title: ''Man of the Family